OL,3,CMan taken to hospital after reports of
OL,4,Can assault at school
OL,6,FOne man has been taken to hospital and
OL,7,Fanother man has been arrested
OL,8,Ffollowing an alleged assault at a
OL,9,Fschool in Port Talbot
OL,11,FOfficers were called to St. Joseph's
OL,12,FRoman Catholic Comprehensive in the
OL,13,FAberavon area this morning at 9:50am.
OL,15,FA 51-year-old male was taken to
OL,16,Fhospital, but his injuries are not
OL,17,Fbelieved to be life changing or life
OL,18,Fthreatening.
OL,20,FA 54-year-old is being questioned on
OL,21,Fsuspicion of assault.
