OL,3,CMan taken to hospital after reports of
OL,4,Can assault at school
OL,6,FIn an email from the Assistant
OL,7,FHeadteacher Mr Torrance, parents were
OL,8,Ftold that an incident had occurred but
OL,9,Fno pupils were involved
OL,11,FIt stated: "The matter is currently
OL,12,Funder investigation by the police, and
OL,13,Fthe school are fully cooperating with
OL,14,Ftheir inquiries.
OL,16,F"We understand that this situation may
OL,17,Fcause concern within our school
OL,18,Fcommunity, and we would like to
OL,19,Freassure you that pupil and staff
OL,20,Fwelfare is our top priority."
